ience-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Evideo%20podcasting%20space%20is%20particularly%20popular%20%E2%80%94%20and%20lucrative%20right%20now%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20prominent%20creators%20like%20Alix%20Earle%20and%20Jake%20Shane%2C%20recently%20launching%20their%20own%20ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedrum.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F06%2F06%2Fspotify-s-2024-podcast-trends-sight-meets-sound-the-rise-the-podfluencer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20report%20from%20Spotify%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20June%20found%20that%2063%25%20of%20respondents%20trust%20their%20favorite%20podcast%20host%20more%20than%20their%20other%20favorite%20influencer.%20It's%20also%20lucrative%20for%20creators%20to%20branch%20out%20into%20audio%3B%20the%20same%20report%20found%20that%2048%25%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20and%20millennials%20said%20they're%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20interested%20in%20ads%20and%20products%20when%20they're%20promoted%20by%20their%20favorite%20podcasters.%20This%20means%20creators%20who%20choose%20to%20host%20podcasts%20can%20tap%20into%20a%20new%20stream%20of%20income%20by%20making%20money%20from%20the%20ads%20promoted%20within%20each%20episode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETu%20said%20that%20moving%20into%20video%20podcasting%20wasn't%20just%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20business%20decision%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20was%20to%20save%20her%20significant%20time.%20While%20season%20one%20of%20%26quot%3BNetworth%20%26amp%3B%20Chill%26quot%3B%20gained%20over%202%20million%20downloads%2C%20Tu%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20her%20day%20creating%20separate%20social%20assets%20to%20promote%20the%20podcast%20because%20it%20was%20only%20audio.%20With%20video%20podcasts%2C%20she%20can%20now%20quickly%20use%20existing%20visual%20clips%20and%20post%20them%20on%20Instagram%2C%20TikTok%2C%20and%20YouTube%20to%20spread%20the%20word%20about%20new%20episodes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20work%20smarter%20so%20I%20didn't%20