tem_625x300_02_October_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcaptain-aged-22-israel-says-1st-soldier-killed-in-lebanon-combat-ops-6700889%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BCaptain%2C%20Aged%2022...%26quot%3B%3A%20Israel%20Says%201st%20Soldier%20Killed%20In%20Lebanon%20Combat%20Ops%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20starters%2C%20let's%20talk%20a%20little%20bit%20about%20Israel's%20Arrow%20system.%20It%20is%20a%20part%20of%20a%20system%2C%20so%20the%20word%20missile%20and%20system%20are%20used%20interchangeably.%20Now%2C%20when%20one%20talks%20about%20SAM%20systems%2C%20you%20have%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20range%20and%20the%20altitude%20it%20can%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20Arrow%20system%20can%20intercept%20incoming%20ballistic%20missiles%20in%20the%20exosphere%2C%20just%20outside%20the%20atmosphere.%20It%20has%20a%20range%20of%202%2C000%20to%202%2C400%20km.%20It%20can%20fly%20to%20an%20altitude%20of%20a%20whopping%20100%20km%3B%20perhaps%20it's%20the%20most%20advanced%20system%20of%20its%20class%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20other%20systems%20presumably%20used%20to%20intercept%20Iranian%20missiles%20last%20night.%20Let's%20look%20at%20the%20next%20one%2C%20which%20is%20David's%20Sling%20system.%20It%20can%20fly%20to%20a%20range%20of%20300%20km%20and%20an%20altitude%20of%20about%2015-odd%20km%20in%20making%20interceptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20finally%2C%20what%20we%20all%20talk%20about%20is%20the%20Iron%20Dome.%20It's%20a%20relatively%20short%20range%20missile%20system.%20In%20fact%2C%20when%20one%20speaks%20about%20what%20Israel%20has%2C%20people%20say%20it's%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20in%20action.%20But%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20entire%20missile%20defence%20tier%20and%20the%20last%20line%20of%20defence.%20It%20can%20fly%20to%20an%20altitude%20of%2010%20km%20and%20has%20a%20range%20of%20about%2070%2