-56db027b629a%5C%22%3ESound%20and%20fit%20concerns%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBrowne%20said%20that%20the%20bass%20and%20treble%2C%20or%20the%20low%20and%20high%20frequencies%20of%20sounds%2C%20are%20generally%20adequate%20on%20the%20Max%2C%20but%20the%20mid-range%20sounds%20are%20where%20the%20headphones%20fall%20flat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20big%20issue%20is%20those%20mid-range%20sounds%20where%20people's%20voices%20are%2C%20where%20a%20guitar%20would%20be%2C%20where%20most%20of%20the%20interesting%20parts%20of%20a%20song%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Browne%20said%20he%20found%20that%20the%20experience%20of%20listening%20to%20the%20British%20band%20Metronomy%2C%20who%20use%20real%20instruments%2C%20was%20distorted%20by%20the%20AirPods%20Max.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20was%20just%20flooring%20to%20me%2C%20how%20little%20of%20the%20instrumentation%20you%20could%20hear%20and%20how%20weirdly%20placed%20his%20voice%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20audio%20science%20enthusiast%2C%20Douglas%20Stephens%2C%20who%20goes%20by%20%26quot%3BDMS%26quot%3B%20online%20and%20reviews%20audio%20equipment%20for%20Headphones.com%2C%20agreed%20that%20the%20sound%20quality%20when%20listening%20to%20music%20on%20the%20AirPods%20Max%20was%20lacking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStephens%2C%20who%20previously%20owned%20a%20recording%20studio%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20resulting%20sound%20was%20%26quot%3Bunnatural%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmuffled%26quot%3B%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20treble%20response%20while%20%26quot%3Bbright%20and%20piercing%26quot%3B%20in%20other%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20have%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40oliviadaytonn%2Fvideo%2F7369714401970048299%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomplained%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdiscussions.apple.com%2Fthread%2F252194577%3FsortBy%3Drank%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efit%20of%20the%20headphones%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20long%20durations.%20Stephens%20said%20it%20could%20be%20due%20to%20the%20way%20the%20headband%20connects%20to%20the%20ear%20cushions%2C%20suggesting%20the%20design%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Blooks%20pretty%2C%26quot%3B%20may%20%26quot%3Bapply%20uneven%20pressure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Apple%20launched%20new%20colors%20and%20added%20a%20USB-C%20charging%20port%20in%20its%20AirPods%20Max%20refresh%20in%20September%2C%20there's%20still%20no%20way%20to%20actually%20turn%20the%20headphones%20off.%20Instead%2C%20users%20can%20only%20set%20them%20to%20low%20power%20mode%20by%20either%20putting%20them%20down%20for%205%20minutes%20or%20placing%20them%20in%20the%20accompanying%20Smart%20Case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Apple%20AirPods%20Max%20(smart%20case)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fcf89e0037cbd001861472f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222143%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20AirPods%20Max%20Smart%20Case.%3Cp%3EApple%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20put%20them%20on%20my%20desk%2C%20and%20they'll%20be%20dead%20when%20I%20go%20to%20pick%20them%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Browne%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20longer%20periods%20without%20using%20the%20headphones%2C%20which%20offer%20up%20to%2020%20hours%20of%20battery%20life%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%2072%20stationary%20hours%20out%20of%20the%20case%2C%20the%20AirPods%20Max%20will%20be%20set%20to%20an%20even%20lower%20power%20mode%20that%20turns%20off%20Bluetooth%20and%20Find%20Me.%20But%20the%20Smart%20Case%20%E2%80%94%20a%20unique%20design%20that%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-airpods-max-carrying-case-jokes-comparisons-purse-bra-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompared%20to%20a%20purse%20or%20bra%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20does%20not%20actually%20charge%20the%20headphones%20itself%2C%20which%20still%20requires%20a%20cord%20to%20charge%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227899c2d4-58b6-4a46-9ec8-8e6f3d076df4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20headphones%20do%20have%20their%20perks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBrowne%20and%20Stephens%20said%20that%20there%20are%20areas%20where%20the%20AirPods%20Max%20shines.%20Like%20the%20other%20AirPods%2C%20they%20said%20the%20AirPods%20Max%20offers%20an%20outstanding%20experience%20with%20active%20noise%20cancellation%2C%20spatial%20audio%2C%20and%20transparency%20modes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPersonally%2C%20I%20think%20that%20their%20transparency%20mode%20is%20the%20best%20that%20I've%20ever%20heard%20in%20a%20product%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20Stephens%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20definitely%20would%20describe%20them%20as%20class-leading%20for%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20one%20aspect%20of%20the%20transparency%20mode%20that%20is%20%26quot%3Bparticularly%20well%20designed%26quot%3B%20is%20its%20ability%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20direction%20of%20outside%20noise%20very%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20actually%20particularly%20easy%2C%20compared%20to%20others%2C%20to%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20in%20the%20transparency%20mode%20if%20someone%20is%20behind%20you%20is%20talking%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20the%20sound%20is%20coming%20from%20behind%20you%2C%20which%20is%20really%20cool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple's%20top-notch%20active%20noise%20cancellation%20(ANC)%20similarly%20shines%20with%20the%20AirPods%20Max%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIts%20ability%20to%20silence%20noise%20from%20the%20outside%20is%20the%20highest%20of%20anything%20ever%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20Browne%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20overall%2C%20Browne%20said%20that%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bso%20many%20better%20options%20for%20so%20m