%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20left%2C%20my%20skin%20in%202022.%20On%20right%2C%20how%20I%20look%20exactly%20two%20years%20later.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAt%2031%2C%20I%20still%20didn't%20have%20a%20real%20skincare%20routine%20and%20didn't%20even%20wear%20daily%20sunscreen.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20had%20forehead%20lines%2C%20oily%20skin%2C%20and%20dark%20spots%20from%20acne%20that%20made%20me%20self-conscious.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20started%20learning%20more%20about%20products%20like%20vitamin%20C%20serum%2C%20and%20best%20practices%20for%20Botox.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2031%2C%20I%20had%20no%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanti-aging-skincare-routine-botox-alternative-dermatologists-advice-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskincare%20routine%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20paint%20a%20clearer%20(and%20grimmer)%20picture%2C%20I%20thought%20my%20SPF%2015%20foundation%20was%20enough%20to%20protect%20my%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbotox-vs-face-taping-wrinkles-skincare-anti-aging-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eself-conscious%20about%20my%20forehead%20lines%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20post-acne%20dark%20spots%2C%20yet%20overwhelmed%20by%2012-step%20nighttime%20regimens.%20But%20when%20I%20started%20covering%20skincare%20for%20my%20job%2C%20I%20began%20absorbing%20the%20advice%20dermatologists%20gave%20in%20interviews.%20They%20didn't%20agree%20on%20every%20product%2C%20but%20they%20overlapped%20on%20a%20few%20big%20points%2C%20like%20the%20importance%20of%20wearing%20sunscreen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20my%20skin%20aged%20backward.%20I%20no%20longer%20have%20the%20same%20issues%20with%20hyperpigmentation%20and%20a%20patchy%20complexion.%20I%20don't%20feel%20as%20oily%2C%20and%20my%20lines%20have%20definitely%20faded.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20I'm%20much%20more%20confident%2C%20often%20going%20makeup-free.%20I%20stopped%20zooming%20in%20on%20every%20candid%20photo%20taken%20of%20me%2C%20obsessing%20over%20every%20imperfection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20now%20follow%20a%20basic%20routine%20(half%20of%20which%20involves%20drugstore%20products).%20Being%20consistent%20has%20not%20only%20transformed%20my%20skin%20over%20time%20but%20also%20given%20me%20peace%20of%20mind%20that%20I'm%20properly%20caring%20for%20my%20body's%20biggest%20organ.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b31e825-f2d0-47ab-873b-ee59605e35f0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20I%20found%20a%20sunscreen%20I%20love%20putting%20on%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22997%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22EltaMD%20UV%20Clear%20sunscreen%20with%20no%20makeup%20(left)%20and%20with%20makeup%20(right).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66faffa47518aa57bc9f6f55%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22747%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEltaMD%20UV%20Clear%20sunscreen%20with%20no%20makeup%20(left)%20and%20with%20makeup%20(right).%20I%20love%20how%20well%20it%20layers%20under%20foundation%20without%20getting%20greasy.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20why%20I%20hated%20putting%20on%20daily%20sunscreen%20was%20how%20unpleasant%20it%20was.%20Most%20over-the-counter%20facial%20sunscreens%20felt%20greasy%20and%20time-consuming%20to%20fully%20rub%20in%2C%20so%20I%20was%20very%20inconsistent%20in%20wearing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20dermatologist%20I've%20interviewed%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20using%20sunscreen%20with%20at%20least%20SPF%2030%20every%20day%2C%20including%20re-applications.%20A%20few%20recommended%20EltaMD%2C%20which%20costs%20around%20%2440%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20I%20would%20ever%20want%20to%20pay%20for%20sunscreen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20trying%20it%20once%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felta-md-sunscreen-review-glass