%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113877493.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMillions%20of%20Ukrainians%20are%20internally%20displaced%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20with%20Russia%2C%20with%20temporary%20modular%20housing%20providing%20crucial%20shelter.%20Many%2C%20like%20elderly%20residents%20in%20Lviv%2C%20face%20tremendous%20loss%20and%20uncertainty%2C%20while%20hoping%20for%20the%20chance%20to%20rebuild%20their%20lives%20amidst%20the%20relentless%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22U%20Sudhakar%20Reddy%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwar-and-displacement-the-human-toll-on-ukraines-internally-displaced-persons%2Farticleshow%2F113877493.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwar-and-displacement-the-human-toll-on-ukraines-internally-displaced-persons%2Famp_articleshow%2F113877493.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwar-and-displacement-the-human-toll-on-ukraines-internally-displaced-persons%2Famp_articleshow%2F113877493.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAbove%20My%20Pay%20Grade%26quot%3B%3A%20Ashwin's%20Blunt%20Take%20After%20Debate%20On%20Test%20Centers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPremier%20off-spinner%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20on%20Tuesday%20agreed%20that%20having%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20Test%20centres%20helps%20the%20players%20but%20fell%20short%20of%20endorsing%20the%20idea%20for%20India%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20above%20his%20pay%20grade%20to%20comment%20on%20that.%20The%20debate%20on%20Test%20centres%20was%20reignited%20after%20Kanpur's%20Green%20Park%20stadium%20came%20under%20criticism%20for%20a%20poor%20drainage%20system%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20loss%20of%20full%20two%20days%20in%20the%20second%20game%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh.%20Star%20batter%20Virat%20Kohli%20had%20suggested%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20that%20India%20should%20have%20five%20major%20Test%20centres%20like%20Australia%20and%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoes%20it%20help%20a%20player%20if%20you%20have%20just%20a%20few%20Test%20centres%3F%20Most%20certainly%20it%20does%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said%20after%20India%20trounced%20Bangladesh%20by%20seven%20wickets%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20when%20we%20go%20to%20Australia%2C%20they%20play%20India%20only%20at%20five%20Test%20centres.%20They%20don't%20play%20us%20in%20Canberra.%20They%20don't%20play%20us%20at%20any%20of%20the%20other%20venues%20where%20they%20won't%20be%20very%20familiar%20with%20the%20conditions.%20So%20do%20England.%20They%20have%20select%20Test%20centres%20and%20that's%20where%20they%20play.%20Some%20of%20those%20are%20only%20white-ball%20centres.%20Can%20we%20do%20it%20here%20(in%20India)%3F%20That's%20above%20my%20pay%20grade.%20I%20cannot%20comment%20on%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20player%20of%20the%20series%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advantage%20of%20playing%20at%20the%20only%20select%20Test%20centres%20is%20that%20the%20players%20are%20familiar%20with%20the%20conditions%20and%20know%20what%20exactly%20they%20would%20require%20to%20do%20at%20a%20specific%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia%20have%20a%20tradition%20of%20playing%20at%20Melbourne%2C%20Sydney%2C%20Perth%2C%20Brisbane%20and%20Adelaide.%20England%20have%20London%2C%20Birmingham%2C%20Manchester%2C%20Nottingham%20and%20Edgbaston%20as%20their%20major%20Test%20centres.%20Before%20saying%20that%20having%20limited%20Test%20centres%20indeed%20helps%2C%20Ashwin%20elaborated%20how%20cricket%20benefits%20by%20having%20various%20venues%20for%20the%20traditional%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirstly%2C%20what%20are%20the%20benefits%20that%20Indian%20cricketers%20attain%20by%20having%20so%20many%20Test%20centers%20are%2C%20you%20have%20got%20cricketers%20who%20come%20and%20play%20Test%20cricket%20from%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20this%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20huge%20country%20and%20it%20has%20triggered%20that%20sort%20of%20urgency%20and%20that%20sort%20of%20passion%20amongst%20cricketers%20to%20be%20able%20to%20come%20and%20play%20for%20this%20country.%20That%20is%20a%20big%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20second%20of%20it%20is%20there%20are%20certain%20requisite%20ingredients%20that%20go%20into%20making%20a%20Test%20match%20happen.%20Like%2C%20for%20the%20weather%20and%20the%20kind%20of%20drainage%20that%20we%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20invest%20on.%20These%20are%20no-brainers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20making%20it%20clear%20that%20there%20should%20not%20be%20any%20compromise%20on%20required%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20young%20opener%20Yashaswi%20Jaiswal%20and%20Shubhman%20Gill%2C%20Ashwin%20had%20no%20doubt%20that%20they%20were%20stars%20in%20the%20making.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20both%20of%20them%20are%20in%20the%20native%20days%20or%20the%20formative%20years%20of%20playing%20Test%20Cricket%20but%20I%20do%20see%20that%20there%20will%20be%20the%20future%20pillars%20and%20overseas%20shores%20that%20they're%20going%20to%20encounter%20shortly%20will%20also%20enhance%20and%20enrich%20their%20experience%20going%20forward%20in%20their%20wonderful%20Test%20journey.%20They%20both%20are%20special%2C%20we%20all%20know%20that.%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said%20coming%20out%20to%20bat%20with%20an%20ultra%20aggressive%20approach%20was%20a%20plan%20they%20had%20to%20follow%20in%20the%20truncated%20second%20Test.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20how%20Yashasvi%20is%20going%20to%20play%20but%20Rohit%20walked%20out%20and%20just%20tonked%20the%20first%20ball%20for%20six.%20So%20when%20you%20walk%20the%20talk%2C%20obviously%20the%20dressing%20room%20doesn't%20have%20any%20other%20choice%20but%20to%20follow%20that%20same%20pattern.%20We%20have%2050%20runs%20ou