%20to%20go%20with%20a%C2%A0more%20expensive%20pet%20insurance%20plan.%C2%A0I%20picked%20a%20plan%20through%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpet-insurance%2Flemonade-pet-insurance-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELemonade%20Insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20bit%20under%20%2445%20a%20month%2C%20which%20includes%20added%20coverage%20like%20preventive%20care%20and%20exam%20fees.%C2%A0While%20it%20costs%20me%20more%20monthly%2C%20I'm%20glad%20I%20went%20with%20this%20option.%20Here's%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIt%20helped%20me%20afford%20a%20visit%20to%20a%20specialist%20after%20my%20dog's%20injury%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20my%20dog%20hurt%20her%20knee.%20We%20immediately%20took%20her%20to%20our%20local%20vet%20for%20an%20exam%2C%20which%20cost%20%24150.%20The%20local%20vet%20wanted%20to%20do%20additional%20testing%20and%20suggested%20surgery.%20We%20decided%20to%20see%20an%20orthopedic%20specialist%20instead%20of%20moving%20forward%20with%20her%20suggestions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20specialist%20visit%20cost%20us%20%24360.%20Because%20our%20more%20expensive%20pet%20insurance%20policy%20covers%20exams%20and%20pays%2080%25%20of%20bills%20related%20to%20specialty%20care%2C%20something%20the%20less%20expensive%20plan%20does%20not%2C%20we%20only%20owed%20%24102%20after%20both%20visits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20don't%20need%20to%20proceed%20with%20surgery%20right%20now%2C%20if%20we%20do%20need%20it%20in%20the%20future%2C%20it%20could%20cost%20a%20few%20thousand%20dollars.%20Our%20insurance%20plan%20would%20cover%2080%25%20of%20those%20costs%2C%20up%20to%20the%20annual%20limit%20of%20%2420%2C000.%20The%20less%20expensive%20plan%20would%20only%20cover%20costs%20up%20to%20%245%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20and%20we'd%20be%20left%20with%20a%20higher%20bill%20if%20we%20needed%20surgery%2C%20postoperative%20physical%20therapy%2C%20and%20doctor%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%3EIt%20covered%20most%20of%20my%20bill%20when%20I%20had%20to%20take%20my%20dog%20to%20urgent%20care%20twice%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%20I%20had%20two%20instances%20where%20I%20had%20to%20take%20my%20dog%20to%20an%20urgent%20care%20facility.%20The%20first%20time%2C%20she%20ate%20something%20she%20shouldn't%20have%2C%20and%20the%20second%20time%2C%20I%20thought%20she%20had%20scratched%20her%20eye.%20Both%20of%20these%20instances%20happened%20after%20business%20hours%20when%20her%20usual%20vet%20was%20closed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20wait%20until%20the%20next%20day%2C%20I%20took%20her%20to%20a%2024-hour%20urgent%20care%20down%20the%20street.%20The%20bills%20for%20both%20of%20these%20visits%20resulted%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20hundred%20dollars%20each.%20Because%20my%20more%20expensive%20pet%20insurance%20plan%20covers%20emergency%20care%2C%20diagnostics%2C%20and%20accident%20and%20illness%20exams%2C%20it%20covered%2080%25%20of%20these%20bills.%20I%20only%20had%20to%20pay%20the%20remaining%2020%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20less%20expensive%20pet%20insurance%20plan%20I%20was%20considering%20doesn't%20cover%20all%20of%20these%20things%2C%20especially%20the%20accident%20and%20illness%20exams.%20I%20would%20have%20had%20to%20pay%20more%20than%2020%25%20of%20the%20bill%20for%20these%20urgent%20care%20visits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIt%20gives%20me%20peace%20of%20mind%2C%20and%20that's%20worth%20every%20penny%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20pet%20insurance%20plan%20has%20a%20low%20deductible%20of%20%24250.%20I%20usually%20meet%20that%20within%20the%20first%20few%20months%20of%20the%20year.%20After%20that%2C%20it%20covers%2080%25%20of%20most%20costs%20related%20to%20the%20healthcare%20of%20my%20dog%2C%20up%20to%20%2420%2C000%20a%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20robust%20plan%20like%20that%20gives%20me%20peace%20of%20mind%20that%20if%20something%20seems%20wrong%20with%20her%20or%20I%20want%20to%20get%20something%