22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F7ulkal0g_not-today_625x300_02_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20too%20many%20can%20claim%20that%20how%20well%20they%20do%20their%20job%20is%20the%20immediate%20difference%20between%20whether%20someone%20lives%20or%20dies.%20Doctors%2C%20yes.%20Firefighters%2C%20yes.%20Lifeguards%2C%20yes.%20Twenty-four-year-old%20Aliah%20Rupawalla%20was%20none%20of%20these.%20And%20yet%2C%20an%20evening%2C%20she%20found%20herself%20being%20the%20only%20witness%20as%20one%2050-something%20Ashwin%20tottered%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20terrace%20of%20one%20of%20the%20thousands%20of%20high-rises%20that%20make%20up%20Mumbai%20and%20its%20abiding%20loneliness.%20All%20she%20was%20armed%20with%20to%20stop%20him%20from%20taking%20the%20plunge%20was%20a%20phone%2C%20a%20tiny%20desk%20in%20a%20cramped%20room%20populated%20by%20at%20least%20four%20other%20people%2C%20a%20crude%20instruction%20manual%2C%20and%20a%20few%20days%20of%20training.%20It%20isn't%20much%2C%20but%20that's%20all%20one%20usually%20gets%20when%20they're%20working%20at%20one%20of%20India's%20numerous%20cash-strapped%20suicide%20prevention%20centres.%20That%2C%20and%20the%20burden%20of%20dealing%20with%20a%20grave%20responsibility%20all%20by%20themselves.%20This%20is%20what%20Aditya%20Kripalani%2C%20an%20independent%20filmmaker%2C%20set%20out%20to%20spotlight%20in%20his%20award-winning%20film%3Cem%3E%20Not%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEvery%20Call%20Matters%2C%20But%20Few%20Get%20Through%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2014%25%20of%20the%20suicide%20deaths%20that%20the%20world%20sees%20happen%20in%20India.%20In%202021%2C%20India's%20suicide%20rate%20was%2012%20per%20one%20lakh%20population.%20Despite%20such%20staggering%20numbers%2C%20the%20Centre's%20allocation%20of%20Rs%201%2C199%20crore%20towards%20mental%20health%20makes%20up%20just%201%25%20of%20the%20total%20health%20budget%20for%20India.%20How%20much%20of%20that%20goes%20to%20India's%20suicide%20prevention%20helplines%20will%20remain%20anybody's%20guess%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20consolidated%20data.%20Ultimately%20though%2C%20this%20poverty%20of%20resources%2C%20manpower%20and%20political%20will%20ends%20up%20taking%20insidious%20forms%20in%20a%20suicide%20prevention%20centre%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20FactChecker%2C%20an%20India-based%20fact-check%20initiative%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factchecker.in%2Fcontext-check%2Fgovts-mental-health-helpline-offers-little-help-other-suicide-prevention-hotlines-too-face-challenges-834837%5C%22%3Edecided%20to%20find%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20equipped%20the%20state-funded%2024x7%20helpline%20KIRAN%20was.%20The%20group%20of%20researchers%20called%20KIRAN%20over%2040%20times%20across%20five%20days.%20They%20got%20through%20to%20an%20actual%20person%20only%20thrice%2C%20and%20after%20an%20average%20waiting%20time%20of%20over%20a%20minute%20and%20a%20half.%20The%20eight%20other%20non-governmental%20hotlines%20they%20tried%20did%20work%2C%20but%20those%2C%20too%2C%20threw%20up%20challenges.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20psychologists%2C%20but%20rehabilitation%20officers.%20We%20are%20assigned%20by%20the%20government%20to%20work%20as%20helpline%20officers%20as%20additional%20duty%20alongside%20our%20regular%20work.%20We%20find%20it%20most%20challenging%20to%20attend%20calls%20during%20the%20night%20and%20early%20morning%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20volunteer%20told%20researchers.%20Another%20explained%20how%20he%20would%20take%20calls%20even%20while%20driving%20and%20travelling.%20Perhaps%20because%20the%20failure%20to%20receive%20even%20one%20could%20mean%20tragedy.%20Perhaps%20it%20is%20why%20Aliah%2C%20seized%20by%20her%20own%20trauma%20of%20the%20past%2C%20goes%20out%20of%20her%20way%20to%20comfort%20Ashwin%2C%20defying%20her%20supervisor%20%26quot%3BMamata%20madam's%26quot%3B%20instructions%20not%20to%20share%20any%20personal%20information.%20Perhaps%20it%20is%20also%20why%20Mamata%20madam%20advises%20Aliah%20to%20block%20prank%20calls%20instantly.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20one%20caller's%20joke%20stops%20a%20genuine%20caller%20from%20reaching%20us%3F%26quot%3B%20Every%20call%20matters%20when%20it's%20death%20you%20are%20racing%20against.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGuilt%2C%20Frustration%2C%20Burnout%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20has%20been%20and%20is%20still%20being%20written%20about%20India's%20suicide%20epidemic.%20But%20we%20haven't%20even%20begun%20to%20scratch%20the%20surface%20of%20what%20those%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20this%20fight%20have%20to%20contend%20with%3A%20nagging%20guilt%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20powerlessness%2C%20frustration%2C%20emotional%20fatigue%2C%20burnout.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20recently%20had%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20girl%2C%20a%20woman%20in%20her%20early%2020s%2C%20who%20lost%20her%20whole%20family.%20It%20stayed%20with%20me%20and%20it%20was%20also%20the%20first%20time%20I%20was%20actually%20crying%20during%20the%20chat%2C%26quot%3B%20recalled%20a%20Dutch%20volunteer%20who%20was%20part%20of%20a%202021%20study%20published%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EInternational%20Journal%20of%20Qualitative%20Studies%20on%20Health%20and%20Well-Being%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Another%20reflected%2C%20%26quot%3BSunday%20night%2C%20I%20had%20a%20lady%20on%20the%20phone%2C%20who%20was%20really%20depressed.%20Yes%2C%20you%20can%20come%20up%20with%20anything%2C%20but%20I%20just%20know%20that%20it%20won't%20help.%20I%20find%20that%20so%20difficult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Too%20Much%20Emotion%20Can%20Kill'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20other%20end%20of%20this%20spectrum%20is%20absolute%20depersonalisation%2C%20where%20every%20call%20becomes%20routine%20and%20every%20caller%20a%20subject%2C%20to%20be%20dealt%20with%20strictly%20by%20the%20book.%20Somewhere%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20Kripalani's%20film%2C%20Aliah%20is%20told%20by%20Mamata%20madam%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20great%20scope%2C%20but%20too%20much%20emotion%20will%20not%20only%20kill%20the%20caller%20but%20also%20you.%26quot%3B%20Ironically%2C%20it's%20Aliah's%20emotional%20solicitude%20that%20pulls%20Ashwin%20back%20from%20the%20brink.%20One%20wonders%20then%2C%20how%20much%20is%20too%20much%20in%20the%20world%20of%20suicide%20prevention%3F%20What%20to%20do%20when%20mere%20sympathy%20leads%20one%20to%20something%20more%20personal%3F%20At%20what%20point%20does%20one%20caller%20become%20less%20or%20more%20important%20than%20others%3F%20Could%20we%20avoid%20making%20this%20choice%20if%20we%20simply%20were%20more%20equipped%20to%20listen%20to%20each%20caller%3F%20To%20provide%20support%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ebefore%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20grief-stricken%20person%20is%20pushed%20to%20the%20edge%20and%20finds%20herself%20dialling%20a%20suicide%20helpline%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20these%20uneasy%20complexities%20that%20%3Cem%3ENot%20Today%20%3C%2Fem%3Eso%20piercingly%20questions.%20Barely%20any%20work%20in%20cinema%20or%20modern%20literature%20has%20attempted%20to%20explore%20the%20world%20of%20suicide%20prevention%20so%20delicately%3B%20most%20wouldn't%20dare%2C%20it%20doesn't%20make%20for%20a%20'masala'%20script%2C%20after%20all.%20But%20Kripalani%20has%2C%20and%20it%20is%20why%20his%20film%20deserves%20all%20the%20praise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20Assistant%20Editor%2C%20Op-Eds%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B919999666555%5C%22%3E9999666555%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%5C%22%3Ehelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20