ade%20a%20forced%20landing.%20There%20were%20four%20IAF%20personnel%2C%20including%20two%20officers%2C%20aboard%20the%20chopper%20and%20all%20of%20them%20have%20been%20rescued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20helicopter%20made%20the%20forced%20landing%20in%20Naya%20Gaon%20of%20Muzaffarpur's%20Aurai%20division%20on%20Wednesday%20afternoon%20and%20had%20taken%20off%20from%20Darbhanga%20Air%20Force%20Base.%20After%20it%20landed%2C%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20chopper%20was%20submerged%20in%20floodwaters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Principal%20Secretary%20of%20the%20disaster%20management%20department%2C%20Pratyaya%20Amrit%2C%20said%20a%20major%20accident%20was%20averted%20because%20of%20the%20pilot's%20presence%20of%20mind.%20He%20said%20the%20engine%20failed%20and%20the%20pilot%20ensured%20that%20the%20helicopter%20landed%20in%20shallow%20water%20with%20no%20people%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20personnel%20have%20been%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20said%20Mr%20Amrit%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20State%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(SDRF)%20began%20rescue%20operations%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20crash%20was%20reported.%20The%20initial%20rescue%20was%20done%20by%20residents%20of%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20helicopter%20was%20an%20Advanced%20Light%20Helicopter%20(ALH)-Dhruv%2C%20which%20are%20used%20by%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%2C%20Army%20and%20the%20Navy.%20The%20fleets%20of%20these%20helicopters%20were%20recently%20grounded%20twice%20because%20of%20technical%20concerns%20over%20certain%20components.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20two%20pilots%20and%20an%20engineer%20died%20after%20a%20helicopter%20crashed%20in%20Pune.%20The%20chopper%2C%20which%20belonged%20to%20Delhi-based%20firm%20Heritage%20Aviation%2C%20was%20headed%20to%20Mumbai%20and%20police%20said%20dense%20fog%20may%20have%20led%20to%20the%20crash%20but%20the%20actual%20cause%20is%20still%20being%20established.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727864820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%