caption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20help%20of%20these%20public%20representatives%2C%20I%20get%20to%20know%20about%20any%20planned%20child%20marriages%20in%20villages.%20After%20I%20am%20informed%20about%20any%20such%20event%2C%20I%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20girl%20and%20try%20to%20convince%20them%20about%20the%20perils%20of%20early%20marriage.%20Through%20counselling%20alone%2C%20we%20have%20prevented%2020%20marriages%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20counselling%20alone%20is%20insufficient%2C%20I%20seek%20help%20from%20the%20district%20administration.%20I%20inform%20the%20district%20magistrate%2C%20SDM%20(sub%20divisional%20magistrate)%2C%20BDO%20(block%20development%20officer)%2C%20police%2C%20CDPO%20(Child%20Development%20Project%20Officer)%2C%20and%20other%20officers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20tell%20the%20parents%20that%20the%20administration%20will%20file%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20family%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358515%2Fwheat-stalk-painting-from-bahraich-uttar-pradesh-girls-training-early-marriage-entrepreneurship%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echild%20marriage%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330387%2Fias-officer-district-magistrate-saju-vaheed-balika-manch-prevent-child-marriage-south-tripura%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epunishable%20offence%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20then%20get%20an%20affidavit%20signed%20by%20the%20parents%20stating%20that%20they%E2%80%99ll%20not%20marry%20off%20their%20daughters%20until%20they%20are%2018%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusfiq%2C%20Block%20Welfare%20Officer%20foe%20Bahadurganj%20and%20Dighalbank%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20main%20focus%20is%20on%20awareness%20and%20counselling%20families%20and%20young%20ch