5C%22759%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20mural%20depicting%20the%20daily%20life%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Lodhi%2C%20painted%20by%20Aaron%20Glasson.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20mural%20showcasing%20vintage%20Indian%20matchboxes%20embedded%20with%20cryptic%20messages%20(that%20bear%20semblance%20to%20Indian%20public%20service%20announcements)%3B%20murals%20that%20transform%20into%203D%3B%20paintings%20that%20highlight%20the%20perils%20of%20a%20social-media-obsessed%20generation%2C%20or%20those%20that%20reference%20the%20daily%20life%20in%20Lodhi%20%E2%80%94%20carpets%20drying%20on%20the%20terrace%2C%20children%20studying%2C%20and%20sweets%20being%20sold%20in%20plenty%3B%20the%20art%20has%20a%20life%20of%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20emotion%20extends%20to%20everything%20Kureshi%E2%80%99s%20mind%20has%20touched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20walk%20down%20the%20lane%20of%20Hanif%20Kureshi%E2%80%99s%20work%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPoignant%E2%80%9D%20is%20how%20admirers%20of%20%E2%80%98Daku%E2%80%99s%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98Cycle%20of%20Time%E2%80%99%20installation%20describe%20it%20to%20be.%20It%20has%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20the%20viewer.%20Displayed%20at%20the%20India%20Art%20Architecture%20Design%20Biennale%20(IAADB)%20at%20the%20Red%20Fort%20in%20Delhi%20in%202023%2C%20the%20installation%20features%20a%20canopy%20of%20words%20%E2%80%98PAST%20IS%20PRESENT%20IS%20FUTURE%20IS%20PAST%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20trance-inducing%20sequence.%20The%20shadows%20they%20cast%20shift%20in%20tandem%20with%20the%20movement%20of%20the%20Sun%2C%20underscoring%20the%20elusive%20nature%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKureshi%E2%80%99s%20work%20combined%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F291305%2Faravani-art-project-bengaluru-helps-trans-community-tackle-stigma-earn-inco