26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20St%2Bart%20India%20(%40startindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EKureshi%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20is%20immortalised%20in%20the%20sands%20of%20time.%20His%20friends%20and%20admirers%20saw%20him%20as%20someone%20who%20was%20observant%20and%20perceptive%2C%20qualities%20that%20translated%20into%20his%20art.%20Art%20curator%20Rahul%20Bhattacharya%20hailed%20him%20as%20a%20role%20model%20to%20many%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20played%20an%20extremely%20significant%20role%20in%20popularising%20street%20art%20in%20India%20and%20was%20a%20role%20model%20to%20many.%20Right%20from%20the%20beginning%2C%20he%20was%20not%20a%20conventional%20artist.%20He%20was%20constantly%20exploring%20new%20avenues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20to%20this%20end%2C%20Kureshi%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20lives%20on%2C%20not%20just%20in%20his%20body%20of%20work%2C%20but%20in%20the%20bonds%20he%20fostered%20among%20artists%20and%20the%20joy%20of%20people%20living%20on%20the%20street%20whose%20view%20was%20Kureshi%E2%80%99s%20larger-than-life%20canvases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Pictures%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCbkDiOIpoJV%2F%3Fhl%3Den%26img_index%3D3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESt%2Bart%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vogue.in%2Fcontent%2Fremembering-hanif-kureshi-the-artist-who-breathed-life-into-mumbais-streets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERemembering%20Hanif%20Kureshi%2C%20the%20artist%20who%20breathed%20life%20into%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20streets%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20Sadaf%20Shaikh%2C%20P